Subject: Re: [VB] Pulling RGB 
bearings





Tap the bearing back in, take a peice of emery cloth and clean-up the axle 
shaft and take a long

punch and lightly tap the bearing until it comes off. These bearings are 
not a press fit and it

shouldn't take much force to get them off.

